♫ <i>Some waited while some traveled</i> ♫

14
00:01:09,600 --> 00:01:12,400
♫ <i>How far away is our future?</i> ♫

15
00:01:12,400 --> 00:01:15,600
♫ <i>Now, each of us</i> ♫

16
