Then, show up in front of him looking dazzling.

530
00:27:36,888 --> 00:27:39,050
Half the work, twice the effect.

531
00:27:39,050 --> 00:27:43,449
Well. How do I tell him?

532
00:27:44,969 --> 00:27:47,089
Just sending him a text will do. Come on.

533
00:27:47,089 --> 00:27:47,989
Let's go.

534
00:27:47,989 --> 00:27:50,609
What should I text him?

535
00:28:18,150 --> 00:28:22,900
<i>[From Xue. Sunian, something urgent came up. Let's watch the movie another day.]</i>

536
00:28:28,920 --> 00:28:32,020
<i>[What's so urgent?]</i>

537
00:28:33,490 --> 00:28:35,169
Mimi.

538
00:28:35,850 --> 00:28:37,330
Where did it go?

539
00:28:37,330 --> 00:28:40,590
Mimi. Mimi.

540
00:28:43,770 --> 00:28:48,168
Why... This is... It seems a little weird.

541
00:28:51,369 --> 00:28:54,670
I'm still not used to being colleagues with you.

542
00:28:57,110 --> 00:29:00,890
After some time, you'll get used to it.

543
00:29:02,490 --> 00:29:05,690
Go and have fun after you get off work.

544
00:29:05,690 --> 00:29:08,410
Don't spend time alone.

545
00:29:08,410 --> 00:29:10,630
I had a date with Xue.

546
00:29:10,630 --> 00:29:12,609
But something came up.

547
00:29:14,830 --> 00:29:16,988
Well, let's get off work then.

548
00:29:16,988 --> 00:29:18,508
Let's go home together

549
00:29:18,508 --> 00:29:21,250
and make a few dishes when we get home.

550
00:29:23,229 --> 00:29:25,730
Go about your business then.

551
00:29:29,380 --> 00:29:31,600
<i>[Beauty SPA]</i>

552
00:29:32,409 --> 00:29:35,029
Why are you pulling a long face?

553
00:29:35,029 --> 00:29:37,088
Sunian asked what was so urgent.

554
00:29:37,088 --> 00:29:39,709
I don't know how to reply to him.

555
00:29:39,709 --> 00:29:42,469
Say you have a thesis to write.

556
00:29:42,469 --> 00:29:43,888
Is that a good idea?

557
00:29:43,888 --> 00:29:45,268
Studying hard is good, right?

558
00:29:45,268 --> 00:29:46,829
Come on.

559
00:29:49,129 --> 00:29:51,930
What's going on?

560
00:30:04,770 --> 00:30:07,370
- Hello?
- Didn't you go to the movies?

561
00:30:07,370 --> 00:30:09,090
Not with Shao Xue?

562
00:30:09,090 --> 00:30:10,888
She said she had things to do.

563
00:30:10,888 --> 00:30:13,749
I saw her. In a beauty spa.

564
00:30:13,749 --> 00:30:15,110
You must be mistaken.

565
00:30:15,110 --> 00:30:16,729
<i>How's that possible?</i>

566
00:30:16,729 --> 00:30:19,149
She's here with her friend.

567
00:30:19,149 --> 00:30:21,089
<i>Look.</i>

568
00:30:22,169 --> 00:30:23,770
Hello?

569
00:30:24,810 --> 00:30:27,189
Oh, no. Oh, no.

570
00:30:27,189 --> 00:30:28,408
Who were you talking to?

571
00:30:28,408 --> 00:30:30,130
Didn't I tell you? My roommate.

572
00:30:30,130 --> 00:30:31,870
Why are you giggling then?

573
00:30:31,870 --> 00:30:34,629
I pulled an opposite stunt as a matchmaker.

574
00:30:34,629 --> 00:30:35,529
What?

575
00:30:35,530 --> 00:30:36,850
You won't understand.

576
00:30:36,850 --> 00:30:42,049
Look. Sometimes, conflict is the catalyst for love.

577
00:30:42,049 --> 00:30:45,148
Come on. I'm in a good mood. It's on me today.

578
00:30:45,148 --> 00:30:46,748
So what are we going to do?

579
00:30:46,748 --> 00:30:48,530
Nothing over 300 yuan.

580
00:30:48,530 --> 00:30:50,709
That's so stingy of you.

581
00:30:50,709 --> 00:30:55,048
A beauty care package worth over 1,000 yuan is just so comfortable.

582
00:30:55,048 --> 00:30:56,390
Right?

583
00:30:56,390 --> 00:30:58,309
Better than going to the movies, right?

584
00:30:58,309 --> 00:31:02,008
Of course. Way better.

585
00:31:09,670 --> 00:31:11,520
<i>[From Sunian: How's your beauty treatment?]</i>

586
00:31:12,900 --> 00:31:15,810
How does Sunian know that I'm at the spa?

587
00:31:15,810 --> 00:31:16,988
What's going on?

588
00:31:16,988 --> 00:31:20,789
Oh, no. I'll go out and make a phone call.

589
00:31:43,269 --> 00:31:46,570
<i>Sunian, are you busy?</i>

590
00:31:47,449 --> 00:31:48,508
Not as busy as you.

591
00:31:48,508 --> 00:31:52,430
Indeed, I'm at a spa.

592
00:31:52,889 --> 00:31:55,609
I can explain.

593
00:31:56,390 --> 00:31:58,469
Lin Shiyin has a membership card.

594
00:31:58,469 --> 00:32:01,849
It just so happens that there's a free beauty treatment only for today.

595
00:32:01,849 --> 00:32:03,348
So she's more important than me?

596
00:32:03,348 --> 00:32:04,769
No.

597
00:32:04,769 --> 00:32:08,329
This treatment is worth 1,888 yuan. It's free.

598
00:32:08,329 --> 00:32:11,050
There won't be another chance. It's now or never.

599
00:32:11,050 --> 00:32:12,489
Well, I get it then.

600
00:32:12,489 --> 00:32:14,068
Money is more important than me.

601
00:32:14,068 --> 00:32:17,930
Well, go on then. Enjoy yourself.

602
00:32:22,169 --> 00:32:23,309
Oh, no.

603
00:32:23,309 --> 00:32:25,929
Sunian's other personality has shown up.

604
00:32:33,050 --> 00:32:35,009
Applying a facial mask is so crucial.

605
00:32:35,009 --> 00:32:36,289
Don't get distracted.

606
00:32:36,289 --> 00:32:37,268
Look, Sunian.

607
00:32:37,268 --> 00:32:39,590
All of a sudden, I feel like going to the movies.

608
00:32:39,590 --> 00:32:40,608
I want to go so badly.

609
00:32:40,609 --> 00:32:42,230
I'm coming over to see you now.

610
00:32:42,230 --> 00:32:45,329
No. It's boring to go to the movies.

611
00:32:45,329 --> 00:32:47,328
No, it's not! It's fun!

612
00:32:47,328 --> 00:32:49,349
My life depends on this movie.

613
00:32:49,349 --> 00:32:50,709
Don't you say no to me.

614
00:32:50,709 --> 00:32:53,749
If I can't watch this movie today, I'll regret it for the rest of my life.

615
00:32:53,749 --> 00:32:54,690
<i>I'll wipe it off my face now.</i>

616
00:32:54,690 --> 00:32:56,508
<i>After I'm done, I'm coming over to see you.</i>

617
00:32:56,508 --> 00:32:58,368
No. What a waste.

618
00:32:58,368 --> 00:33:01,029
<i>Sunian, I have to relax to enjoy a beauty treatment.</i>

619
00:33:01,029 --> 00:33:02,669
<i>I can't relax if you're not happy.</i>

620
00:33:02,669 --> 00:33:04,729
Besides, with you acting this way, I'm just absorbing toxins.

621
00:33:04,729 --> 00:33:06,928
Think about it. If you won't let me come over, you'll be upset.

622
00:33:06,928 --> 00:33:08,569
The beauty treatment would have just been in vain, and there will be no movie time.

623
00:33:08,569 --> 00:33:11,210
It would be all for nothing.

624
00:33:11,210 --> 00:33:12,729
<i>Sunian, I'm begging you.</i>

625
00:33:12,729 --> 00:33:15,489
<i>Let me come over to see you.</i>

626
00:33:15,489 --> 00:33:17,450
All right then.

627
00:33:17,450 --> 00:33:18,930
I'll wait for you at the cinema.

628
00:33:18,930 --> 00:33:19,940
<i>Be safe.</i>

629
00:33:19,949 --> 00:33:22,709
Well, see you later. See you later.

630
00:33:27,870 --> 00:33:30,989
- Shiyin! I have to go now. Rain check, all right?
- What's the matter?

631
00:33:30,989 --> 00:33:34,009
Sunian is mad. When this guy gets angry, no woman is a match for him.

632
00:33:34,009 --> 00:33:35,489
I have to go. Bye!

633
00:33:35,490 --> 00:33:38,210
Slow down! Don't fall!

634
00:33:46,649 --> 00:33:48,249
<i>Legilimency!</i>

635
00:33:54,849 --> 00:33:56,088
<i>Harry.</i>

636
00:33:56,089 --> 00:33:57,910
<i>Sirius.</i>

637
00:33:58,409 --> 00:34:00,529
<i>I'm going to vomit.</i>

638
00:34:00,530 --> 00:34:02,390
<i>Stop it!</i>

639
00:34:02,390 --> 00:34:05,249
<i>Is this what you call control?</i>

640
00:34:05,249 --> 00:34:06,368
<i>We've been at it for hours!</i>

641
00:34:06,369 --> 00:34:08,049
<i>I can do the breath!</i>

642
00:34:08,049 --> 00:34:12,650
Sunian, would you like some popcorn?

643
00:34:13,149 --> 00:34:14,650
No.

644
00:34:21,750 --> 00:34:25,430
How about milk tea?

645
00:34:26,640 --> 00:34:28,420
<i>My father was a great man.</i>

646
00:34:28,420 --> 00:34:31,740
<i>Your father was a swaggard.</i>

647
00:34:31,740 --> 00:34:34,070
<i>I take after my father.</i>

648
00:34:34,889 --> 00:34:37,030
- Well.
- Watch the movie.

649
00:34:37,030 --> 00:34:38,510
Stop talking.

650
00:34:38,510 --> 00:34:39,930
<i>Come on, Winnie.</i>

651
00:34:39,930 --> 00:34:41,600
<i>Snape!</i>

652
00:34:41,600 --> 00:34:42,630
<i>Billy Armis.</i>

653
00:34:54,640 --> 00:34:56,190
<i>Enough.</i>

654
00:35:01,810 --> 00:35:06,920
Sunian, that movie was pretty good. Right?

655
00:35:08,870 --> 00:35:13,110
Why don't I treat you to another movie tomorrow?

656
00:35:13,110 --> 00:35:14,570
No need.

657
00:35:14,570 --> 00:35:16,290
Go home now.

658
00:35:22,629 --> 00:35:24,489
<i>What do I do?</i>

659
00:35:24,490 --> 00:35:29,549
<i>How did I patch things up with Sunian the last time I pissed him off?</i>

660
00:35:34,710 --> 00:35:37,029
<i>Sunian, please don't be mad.</i>

661
00:35:37,029 --> 00:35:40,128
<i>Next time, I'll save you some candied hawthorn berries.</i>

662
00:35:40,128 --> 00:35:41,310
<i>I'm not eating them.</i>

663
00:35:41,310 --> 00:35:43,149
<i>Then I'll set off fireworks for you.</i>

664
00:35:43,149 --> 00:35:45,109
<i>I'm not watching them.</i>

665
00:35:56,310 --> 00:35:58,069
<i>Does it hurt?</i>

666
00:35:58,069 --> 00:36:00,069
<i>It won't hurt anymore if you stop being mad at me.</i>

667
00:36:00,069 --> 00:36:02,429
<i>Be careful next time.</i>

668
00:36:35,289 --> 00:36:36,830
<i>Sunian!</i>

669
00:36:36,830 --> 00:36:39,170
<i>Open the window and take a look!</i>

670
00:37:15,029 --> 00:37:16,850
Does it hurt?

671
00:37:16,850 --> 00:37:19,550
It won't hurt anymore if you stop being mad at me.

672
00:37:19,550 --> 00:37:21,369
You're still so careless.

673
00:37:21,370 --> 00:37:22,650
Let me take a look.

674
00:37:22,650 --> 00:37:24,809
Promise me. Don't be mad at me.

675
00:37:24,809 --> 00:37:26,850
Then, I'll show you.

676
00:37:29,950 --> 00:37:32,369
All right. I won't be mad.

677
00:37:32,369 --> 00:37:34,909
Look! It doesn't hurt anymore.

678
00:37:38,669 --> 00:37:40,710
Sunian.

679
00:37:40,710 --> 00:37:42,430
Don't be mad anymore.

680
00:37:42,430 --> 00:37:44,429
I promise you.

681
00:37:44,429 --> 00:37:46,870
I won't lie to you again.

682
00:37:46,870 --> 00:37:48,770
Smile, will you?

683
00:37:52,069 --> 00:37:54,269
Sunian.

684
00:37:54,910 --> 00:37:57,230
Sunian.

685
00:37:57,690 --> 00:38:01,510
Sunian.

686
00:38:01,510 --> 00:38:03,080
♫ <i>Missing you</i> ♫

687
00:38:03,080 --> 00:38:06,910
♫ <i>No better place to go, Amour</i> ♫

688
00:38:06,919 --> 00:38:12,030
♫ <i>I even want to hear the birds say, "Miss me."</i> ♫

689
00:38:13,150 --> 00:38:14,730
♫ <i>Missing you</i> ♫

690
00:38:14,730 --> 00:38:18,660
♫ <i>No better things to do, Amour</i> ♫

691
00:38:18,669 --> 00:38:23,520
♫ <i>Why don't you just find me at 3:00?</i> ♫

692
00:38:24,960 --> 00:38:33,259
♫ <i>The sweetest hour starts from the time... we meet</i> ♫

693
00:38:37,450 --> 00:38:39,070
Xue.

694
00:38:39,950 --> 00:38:41,569
What brings you here?

695
00:38:41,569 --> 00:38:43,489
Didn't you go to the movies yesterday?

696
00:38:43,490 --> 00:38:45,049
The beauty salon gave me a few boxes of masks.

697
00:38:45,050 --> 00:38:46,890
So I brought them over for you.

698
00:38:46,890 --> 00:38:48,570
Thank you.

699
00:38:49,689 --> 00:38:52,129
Well, how did the movie go?

700
00:38:52,129 --> 00:38:53,949
Is Sunian still mad?

701
00:38:54,750 --> 00:38:56,529
Not anymore.

702
00:38:57,310 --> 00:39:00,668
Well, is there any progress between you two?

703
00:39:01,410 --> 00:39:03,770
No, not at all.

704
00:39:05,330 --> 00:39:07,448
All right. Enjoy. I'll get going.

705
00:39:07,448 --> 00:39:08,870
Shiyin!

706
00:39:08,870 --> 00:39:11,569
I have a question for you.

707
00:39:14,549 --> 00:39:17,070
Does it make two people closer

708
00:39:17,070 --> 00:39:19,750
when they go from good friends...

709
00:39:20,230 --> 00:39:22,750
to lovers?

710
00:39:24,209 --> 00:39:26,030
Is something going on between you two?

711
00:39:26,030 --> 00:39:28,728
No! Nothing is going on.

712
00:39:28,729 --> 00:39:31,590
I was just asking.

713
00:39:35,870 --> 00:39:39,269
Well, it's hard to say.

714
00:39:39,989 --> 00:39:41,830
Before you get together,

715
00:39:41,830 --> 00:39:45,410
you'll think everything about him is good.

716
00:39:45,410 --> 00:39:48,069
But once your relationship is confirmed,

717
00:39:48,069 --> 00:39:53,150
you will find that it's completely different

718
00:39:53,150 --> 00:39:55,189
from what you thought.

719
00:39:58,669 --> 00:40:02,150
Aren't things going well for you and Wu Huan?

720
00:40:09,350 --> 00:40:11,629
It's a long story.

721
00:40:12,390 --> 00:40:17,130
If two people live in different circles,

722
00:40:18,189 --> 00:40:20,950
they will not have a lot of common topics.

723
00:40:20,950 --> 00:40:23,729
Unlike the time when we were in high school,

724
00:40:23,729 --> 00:40:26,089
spending all day together.

725
00:40:26,089 --> 00:40:30,089
Besides, once you start a relationship,

726
00:40:31,189 --> 00:40:33,449
there's no going back to being friends.

727
00:40:36,390 --> 00:40:41,070
So, Xue, you have to give serious consideration to that question.

728
00:40:53,509 --> 00:40:54,989
Sunian, I'm leaving.

729
00:40:54,989 --> 00:40:57,289
Where are you going at this late hour?

730
00:40:57,289 --> 00:40:59,069
A business meeting.

731
00:41:00,310 --> 00:41:02,269
You seem busy, huh?

732
00:41:25,390 --> 00:41:27,109
Why are you smiling?

733
00:41:30,790 --> 00:41:32,389
I'm not.

734
00:41:32,389 --> 00:41:34,669
Why would you smile for nothing?

735
00:41:34,669 --> 00:41:36,809
Something must be up.

736
00:41:36,809 --> 00:41:38,569
Tell me.

737
00:41:39,870 --> 00:41:41,989
Get back to your games.

738
00:41:58,890 --> 00:42:00,409
Pei Shu.

739
00:42:02,669 --> 00:42:03,750
Let me ask you something.

740
00:42:03,750 --> 00:42:05,190
Ask away.

741
00:42:12,109 --> 00:42:16,269
Well, if two people...

742
00:42:19,230 --> 00:42:21,730
kissed,

743
00:42:22,469 --> 00:42:25,349
does it mean they are together?

744
00:42:25,349 --> 00:42:27,029
You're asking the right person.

745
00:42:27,029 --> 00:42:29,270
I know all about kissing.

746
00:42:29,270 --> 00:42:33,049
Look. Before you kiss a person, you have to first confess your feelings.

747
00:42:33,049 --> 00:42:34,288
She has to say yes first.

748
00:42:34,289 --> 00:42:36,870
If you kiss her before you even confess,

749
00:42:36,870 --> 00:42:40,310
that's considered an indecent act.

750
00:42:42,230 --> 00:42:43,509
Confess?

751
00:42:43,509 --> 00:42:45,269
Who did you kiss?

752
00:42:46,710 --> 00:42:50,050
I'm asking you a question! Who did you kiss?

